Citation Notice version 1.0

This Citation Notice is part of the minor_planet_visibility software suite.

Parties that use ASTRON Software resulting in papers and/or publications are requested to refer to the DOI(s) 
that correspond(s)to the version(s) of the ASTRON Software used:

10.5281/zenodo.2655011

Parties that use ASTRON Software for purposes that do not result in publications
(e.g. commercial parties) are asked toinform ASTRON abouttheir use of ASTRON Software, 
by sending an email to including the DOIs mentioned above in the message.
